body: This is not an issue with TensorFlow - your question is better suited for Stack Overflow. That said, perhaps you could look into using [TensorRT with TF 1.7](https://developers.googleblog.com/2018/03/tensorrt-integration-with-tensorflow.html) to speed up your Mask RCNN inference. This would be just one of many optimizations you could try.
